--- README.md ---
Lab Technician Landing Page

A minimal single-page landing site for a lab technician. The page is responsive, uses a red/black/white color scheme, includes a hero with title and subtitle, a brief services list, and a contact form that shows an alert on submit (no backend).

Features
- Single HTML page
- Responsive mobile-first layout (usable from ~320px to desktop widths)
- Hero section with title and subtitle
- Services list
- Contact form (name, email, message) that triggers an alert on submit
- Color palette limited to red (#ff0000), black (#000000), and white (#ffffff)
- Basic accessibility: labeled form inputs, logical heading structure (h1 > h2), visible focus states, sufficient color contrast for body text

Getting Started
- Open index.html in your browser.
- Click "Contact Me" to jump to the form. Submitting the form displays a simple alert and resets the fields.

Testing
- Requires Node.js (LTS recommended).
- Install dependencies (only Jest is required for the test):
  npm install
- Run tests:
  npm test

Project Structure
- index.html: Single-page content
- styles.css: Responsive styles using only red, black, and white
- script.js: Contact form alert behavior and footer year
- tests/hero-title.test.js: Jest test to ensure the hero title exists

Notes on Accessibility & Contrast
- Body text uses black on white (21:1 contrast).
- Red is used as an accent (borders, interactive states). When red is used as a background (e.g., CTA hover), text remains black to maintain sufficient contrast on red.
- Form inputs have associated labels via for/id attributes. Focus styles are visible and high-contrast.


--- index.html ---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Lab Technician - Professional Services</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
  <script src="script.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to main content</a>
  <header class="hero" role="banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 id="hero-title">Professional Lab Technician</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Reliable lab support with a focus on precision, safety, and timely results.</p>
      <a class="cta-button" href="#contact">Contact Me</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main" class="main-content">
    <section class="services" aria-labelledby="services-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="services-heading">Services</h2>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Sample preparation and processing</li>
          <li>Equipment calibration and maintenance</li>
          <li>Data recording and quality control</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="contact-heading">Get in touch</h2>
        <form id="contact-form" novalidate>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input id="name" name="name" type="text" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="submit-button">Send Message</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer" role="contentinfo">
    <div class="container">
      <small>&copy; <span id="year"></span> Lab Technician</small>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>


